headline: Willis: Rising threats, political evacuations and kidnap shaped the 2025 crisis management landscape
summary: LONDON, Feb. 12, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Incidents involving threats to individuals or client assets increased by more than a third in 2025, accounting for 37% of all incidents reported to Alert:24 – the in-house risk advisory and crisis support service provided by Willis, a WTW business (NASDAQ:WTW).
